<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Fri, 22 Apr 2022 09:41:33 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>歐盟擴大 USB-C 統一接口範圍，適用於電話、平板、相機、耳機、遊戲機</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/04/22/usb-c/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=usb-c</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Harold]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 22 Apr 2022 09:41:33 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[usb-c]]></category><category><![CDATA[歐盟]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1096906</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>近年，USB-C 接口成了主流，減少了使用其他接口。歐盟積極推動手機統一接口，內部市場與消費者保護委員會（IM [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>近年，USB-C 接口成了主流，減少了使用其他接口。歐盟積極推動手機統一接口，內部市場與消費者保護委員會（IMCO）以壓倒性票數通過支持電子裝置統一使用 USB-C 規格的草案，並擴大電子產品接口的統一範圍。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1096913 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/USB-C-Over-Lightning-Feature-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/USB-C-Over-Lightning-Feature-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/USB-C-Over-Lightning-Feature-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/USB-C-Over-Lightning-Feature-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/USB-C-Over-Lightning-Feature-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/USB-C-Over-Lightning-Feature.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：MacRumors</p><p>為避免製造過多電子垃圾，歐盟內部市場和消費者保護委員會週三投票支持該立法，43 票贊成，2 票反對，大比數通過法案。新法案希望消費者在購買電子產品時，省略充電線及充電器。擴大範圍有手機、平板電腦、數碼相機、耳機、遊戲機、便攜式喇叭等。豁免的電子產品只有智能手錶、健康手環、運動周邊產品等。</p><p>近年無線充電亦大行其道，歐盟準備就無線充電立規，望在 2026 年前提出規定，統一無線充電規格。為免造成混淆，歐盟希望廠商能在產品包裝上標明有否含充電器。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2022/04/21/eu-closer-to-mandate-apple-switch-to-usb-c/">MacRumors</a></p><p>&#8212;</p><div id="entry-content-1096569" class="entry-content" data-swiftype-name="body" data-swiftype-type="text"><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk </u></a></p></div></p><div class="feedflare">
